WEBVTT

01:51.950 --> 01:57.630
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.590 --> 02:01.890
[Episode 11]

02:06.770 --> 02:08.169
Since Fan Yun's leaving,

02:08.630 --> 02:10.560
you're leaving too; is that right?

02:17.250 --> 02:18.360
From now on,

02:18.380 --> 02:19.620
I won't get to

02:19.650 --> 02:22.130
see you and Fan Yun whenever I want?

02:23.900 --> 02:24.740
Yes.

02:35.570 --> 02:37.170
What's wrong with you today?

02:40.260 --> 02:41.910
When I'm quiet,

02:41.980 --> 02:43.510
don't I seem like a firefly?

02:49.980 --> 02:51.540
Let me tell you something.

02:51.570 --> 02:53.820
Actually, my name wasn't Wei Shisan,

02:53.840 --> 02:54.750
but Wei Ying.

02:55.120 --> 02:55.840
Wei Ying?

02:56.550 --> 02:57.750
"Ying" as in firefly.

02:57.780 --> 02:58.710
Special, right?

03:00.090 --> 03:01.560
They use their tails to emit light

03:01.560 --> 03:03.490
and illuminate others in the dark.

03:04.970 --> 03:05.920
Actually,

03:05.940 --> 03:07.270
I used to wonder

03:07.350 --> 03:08.630
if there'd be someone

03:08.650 --> 03:10.110
who would come into my life

03:10.370 --> 03:11.580
and say to me,

03:12.280 --> 03:12.910
"Ying,

03:13.440 --> 03:15.020
you're like a firefly.

03:15.260 --> 03:16.230
Only I can

03:16.450 --> 03:17.710
call you by this name."

03:19.400 --> 03:20.590
But now, I realize

03:20.610 --> 03:22.740
I don't want to be a firefly

03:22.770 --> 03:23.950
who illuminates others.

03:23.950 --> 03:25.130
I want to be like Fan Yun,

03:25.130 --> 03:26.730
doing everything I want to do,

03:26.730 --> 03:28.460
without overthinking things.

03:30.910 --> 03:31.680
That's nice.

03:34.090 --> 03:35.130
So,

03:35.150 --> 03:36.530
let's keep this Wei Ying name

03:36.530 --> 03:38.530
as our secret.

03:40.500 --> 03:42.300
Are you making this up to fool me?

03:42.360 --> 03:43.329
I'm not.

03:45.620 --> 03:46.410
Alright.

03:46.940 --> 03:48.100
Then I wish you

03:48.130 --> 03:49.520
and Fan Yun

03:49.540 --> 03:51.030
achieve what you desire.

04:06.040 --> 04:07.130
Your eyes are

04:07.240 --> 04:08.300
really beautiful.

04:09.950 --> 04:10.670
Miss Wei.

04:10.700 --> 04:11.900
Call me Wei Shisan.

04:18.990 --> 04:19.790
Say it.

04:21.120 --> 04:22.190
Wei Shisan.

04:25.030 --> 04:26.350
You know what?

04:26.380 --> 04:27.280
When I was little,

04:27.280 --> 04:29.190
I did something really embarrassing.

04:29.190 --> 04:30.040
What is it?

04:30.930 --> 04:31.720
Well,

04:33.730 --> 04:35.810
I used to wet the bed a lot.

04:36.480 --> 04:37.710
Wet the bed?

05:15.540 --> 05:18.680
♪ Watch how many flowers
bloom and wither ♪

05:19.100 --> 05:22.530
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

05:22.900 --> 05:25.460
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

05:31.520 --> 05:35.010
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

05:35.420 --> 05:38.610
♪ Feelings that can't be severed ♪

05:39.080 --> 05:41.830
♪ How to let go? ♪

05:47.580 --> 05:50.930
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

05:51.450 --> 05:55.110
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

05:55.680 --> 05:57.400
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

05:56.280 --> 05:58.110
I hope the Nine Cities

05:57.810 --> 06:03.360
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

05:58.130 --> 06:01.010
can grow prosperous and grand

06:01.040 --> 06:03.240
like this sapling does,

06:03.260 --> 06:04.430
to protect and bless the people.

06:03.740 --> 06:05.230
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

06:05.270 --> 06:07.610
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

06:07.770 --> 06:10.940
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

06:11.220 --> 06:13.440
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

06:13.460 --> 06:15.830
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

06:15.860 --> 06:19.560
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

06:19.870 --> 06:21.210
♪ For whom does ♪

06:21.230 --> 06:23.400
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

06:23.430 --> 06:27.400
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

06:27.630 --> 06:29.680
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

06:28.800 --> 06:30.600
Within the borders of the Qi Residence,

06:29.710 --> 06:32.100
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

06:31.510 --> 06:34.360
even surviving is not easy,

06:32.420 --> 06:39.900
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

06:34.710 --> 06:36.480
let alone

06:36.510 --> 06:38.470
building a career.

06:41.240 --> 06:41.930
So,

06:42.710 --> 06:44.270
for a better Nine Cities,

06:44.890 --> 06:46.450
let's keep working hard,

06:46.480 --> 06:47.450
Fan Yun.

06:59.720 --> 07:00.560
Gao Ran?

07:01.600 --> 07:02.560
Why are you here?

07:03.720 --> 07:04.660
To take you home.

07:05.250 --> 07:06.520
But you're not

07:06.540 --> 07:07.630
on duty today.

07:08.570 --> 07:09.720
To be honest,

07:09.750 --> 07:11.080
I've already resigned.

07:11.380 --> 07:12.330
Where you are,

07:12.360 --> 07:13.530
I will naturally be.

07:15.690 --> 07:16.930
Come on.

07:18.090 --> 07:19.090
Let's go home.

07:19.120 --> 07:20.340
You're such a good friend.

07:20.340 --> 07:21.220
I'm grateful.

07:21.390 --> 07:21.920
Let's go.

07:22.780 --> 07:23.580
Let's go home.

08:04.930 --> 08:05.550
Gao Ran,

08:06.240 --> 08:07.230
I'll have a quick word

08:07.230 --> 08:08.290
with the governor.

08:08.300 --> 08:09.720
Wait for me at the gate.

08:31.920 --> 08:33.480
Your Exc...

08:35.140 --> 08:36.059
You are

08:36.400 --> 08:37.400
leaving already?

08:43.799 --> 08:44.610
Qi Zheng.

08:45.390 --> 08:46.590
After parting today,

08:47.160 --> 08:49.220
our relationship as husband and wife

08:50.200 --> 08:51.540
is completely over.

08:52.250 --> 08:53.110
From now on,

08:53.390 --> 08:55.390
you must take good care of yourself.

08:56.150 --> 08:56.960
Also,

08:58.540 --> 09:00.030
stop being so stubborn.

09:00.050 --> 09:02.200
Go ask Lord Jiang for a prescription,

09:02.230 --> 09:02.870
and he'll cure...

09:02.870 --> 09:04.670
Everything that happened today

09:06.580 --> 09:07.990
was part of the plan.

09:11.000 --> 09:12.270
But in my heart...

09:21.360 --> 09:22.150
Never mind.

09:24.510 --> 09:25.550
From now on,

09:26.150 --> 09:27.880
take good care of yourself too.

09:33.520 --> 09:34.170
By the way,

09:35.310 --> 09:36.280
look at this.

09:36.300 --> 09:38.100
I've finished embroidering it.

09:38.920 --> 09:40.010
Consider it

09:40.550 --> 09:41.760
a parting gift.

09:56.840 --> 09:58.500
I also have something for you.

09:59.220 --> 10:00.070
What is it?

10:02.780 --> 10:05.390
♪ Tear the dark night apart ♪

10:05.410 --> 10:07.090
♪ Turn my whole heart ♪

10:07.120 --> 10:09.120
♪ Into an ever-burning bright lamp light ♪

10:09.140 --> 10:11.810
♪ Live up to every year ♪

10:11.830 --> 10:15.060
♪ With fiery passion ♪

10:15.210 --> 10:17.990
♪ Even if I merge into ♪

10:18.010 --> 10:19.720
♪ The stream of stars in the end ♪

10:19.740 --> 10:22.010
♪ With thousands of miles between us ♪

10:22.030 --> 10:28.050
♪ I never fade away within your eyes ♪

10:33.000 --> 10:34.460
I'll wait for your return.

10:50.070 --> 10:50.860
You...

10:52.240 --> 10:53.030
I...

10:55.360 --> 10:56.870
Stupid Qi Zheng!

10:56.040 --> 10:59.780
♪ As long as the heart's light remains ♪

11:00.640 --> 11:10.650
♪ There won't be loneliness ♪

11:17.290 --> 11:19.200
[Qingteng Academy]

11:18.390 --> 11:19.720
"Having not seen you for days,

11:19.720 --> 11:21.070
I miss you so very much.

11:21.420 --> 11:23.660
Hope you are well in the summer.

11:23.780 --> 11:25.520
Remember to stay hydrated.

11:25.830 --> 11:27.610
From the anonymous one who is concerned"?

11:27.610 --> 11:29.340
There's more! This letter too!

11:29.410 --> 11:31.220
I need to practice this one more.

11:32.320 --> 11:33.480
Quiet down!

11:36.530 --> 11:37.860
I just didn't want to

11:37.890 --> 11:39.390
waste paper, so I gave it to you

11:39.390 --> 11:41.520
for writing practice on the back side.

11:43.070 --> 11:44.070
From now on,

11:44.090 --> 11:45.020
no more talking.

11:45.240 --> 11:46.750
Focus on your writing practice,

11:46.750 --> 11:47.630
you hear me?

12:20.760 --> 12:21.640
Yun.

12:23.250 --> 12:23.840
Tell me,

12:23.870 --> 12:26.490
how many chicks can hatch from these eggs?

12:31.320 --> 12:33.170
It's useless no matter how many hatch.

12:33.170 --> 12:35.100
What? H-How is it useless?

12:35.130 --> 12:36.290
Look, look;

12:36.310 --> 12:37.530
chicks will hatch and lay eggs,

12:37.530 --> 12:38.830
and chicks will hatch and lay eggs.

12:38.830 --> 12:40.760
We will be so rich!

12:46.180 --> 12:46.890
Yun,

12:46.930 --> 12:48.460
look. This is quite fun too.

12:48.480 --> 12:49.050
Look.

13:02.900 --> 13:04.450
That looks quite like you.

13:05.520 --> 13:06.210
No way.

13:06.930 --> 13:07.890
Not at all.

13:13.210 --> 13:14.210
Your Excellency.

13:17.690 --> 13:18.690
Your Excellency.

13:25.280 --> 13:26.160
Fan Yun?

13:26.650 --> 13:27.770
You're back!

13:30.170 --> 13:31.240
Your Excellency.

13:31.260 --> 13:32.890
Look at my wedding dress.

13:33.430 --> 13:34.310
Do I look good?

13:35.330 --> 13:36.000
By the way,

13:36.720 --> 13:38.480
I have a secret to tell you.

13:40.460 --> 13:41.550
I'm about to

13:41.670 --> 13:43.320
get married with

13:43.340 --> 13:44.620
Young Master Lou Qiyan

13:44.650 --> 13:45.720
very soon.

13:47.090 --> 13:48.160
Come here. Quick.

13:48.190 --> 13:48.760
Come on.

13:51.680 --> 13:52.480
That's right.

13:53.040 --> 13:54.900
We're getting married very soon.

13:58.000 --> 13:59.080
And then,

13:59.590 --> 14:01.120
Young Master Qiyan and I

14:01.140 --> 14:02.210
will be together,

14:02.240 --> 14:04.030
making a lot of money

14:04.580 --> 14:06.740
and having a lot of children.

14:07.160 --> 14:08.780
Please rest assured, Your Excellency.

14:08.780 --> 14:10.980
Please rest assured, Your Excellency.

14:47.630 --> 14:48.780
Why is

14:48.800 --> 14:50.370
the door unlocked?

14:51.250 --> 14:52.210
Is it because

14:52.730 --> 14:53.610
Dad is at home?

15:02.250 --> 15:03.650
-Let's go.
-He's at home.

15:06.060 --> 15:06.910
Dad!

15:10.690 --> 15:11.480
Lord Fan Qi.

15:11.500 --> 15:12.200
Dad!

15:13.280 --> 15:14.240
Dad!

15:14.260 --> 15:15.290
-I'm here!
-I clearly hear him...

15:15.290 --> 15:16.410
I'm here!

15:16.430 --> 15:17.030
It's fine.

15:17.060 --> 15:18.720
Everything is under control!

15:19.400 --> 15:19.770
You...

15:19.770 --> 15:20.770
It's on fire, Dad!

15:21.000 --> 15:21.670
Hurry!

15:24.150 --> 15:26.390
I just wanted to make you
rice cooked in bamboo,

15:26.390 --> 15:27.910
but a little accident happened.

15:27.910 --> 15:29.300
-This...
-Dad.

15:29.390 --> 15:30.030
Just

15:30.030 --> 15:31.430
leave the cooking to us.

15:31.450 --> 15:32.600
You go out first. Hurry up.

15:32.600 --> 15:33.350
Go on.

15:37.810 --> 15:40.010
Your Excellency, what's the occasion?

15:41.030 --> 15:41.750
Normally,

15:41.750 --> 15:43.720
isn't it Lord Zheng
who plays chess with you?

15:43.720 --> 15:44.600
Why did you

15:44.620 --> 15:46.220
ask me to play with you today?

15:47.360 --> 15:48.990
Lord Zheng is swamped with work,

15:48.990 --> 15:50.720
so I didn't want to disturb him.

15:51.760 --> 15:52.760
Yes, yes.

15:54.800 --> 15:57.240
It must be tough for Lord Zheng,
working so hard

15:57.240 --> 15:59.020
for the Nine Cities every day.

15:59.050 --> 16:00.500
Especially since

16:00.720 --> 16:02.000
this year's selection exam

16:02.000 --> 16:03.440
is about to begin,

16:04.270 --> 16:05.700
he has even less time.

16:07.560 --> 16:09.360
I invited you here today because

16:10.050 --> 16:11.370
I want to play a game of

16:12.700 --> 16:14.100
Five-in-a-Row with you.

16:15.280 --> 16:16.400
Five-in-a-Row?

16:19.950 --> 16:22.240
Isn't that too childish?

16:22.260 --> 16:25.380
This is not suitable for
the great Huiyun Pavilion.

16:27.850 --> 16:29.180
If you can play it with Elder Zheng,

16:29.180 --> 16:30.390
why not with me?

16:34.390 --> 16:35.390
Your Excellency,

16:35.650 --> 16:37.710
you know I play chess with Lord Zheng?

16:38.740 --> 16:40.480
You're all my right-hand men.

16:40.810 --> 16:42.430
Of course I have to
take special care of you.

16:42.430 --> 16:43.070
Come on.

16:43.260 --> 16:44.670
OK, OK.

16:45.110 --> 16:46.710
After you, Your Excellency.

16:56.630 --> 16:57.680
Your Excellency,

16:58.280 --> 16:59.920
this move of yours

16:59.950 --> 17:01.700
is not too wise.

17:03.150 --> 17:05.829
If it's cut off by my piece like this,

17:05.829 --> 17:08.200
I'm afraid it can't be salvaged.

17:09.750 --> 17:11.280
Since it can't be salvaged,

17:11.880 --> 17:13.160
I'll find another way.

17:20.069 --> 17:21.069
Your Excellency,

17:21.349 --> 17:24.000
if you played this game with Lord Zheng,

17:24.859 --> 17:26.339
he wouldn't let you

17:26.369 --> 17:28.210
place a piece here so easily.

17:32.510 --> 17:33.830
Then what if

17:34.550 --> 17:36.220
you lend me a hand, Lord Lyu?

17:37.110 --> 17:39.510
No one else
could do anything about it then.

17:46.030 --> 17:47.400
I'm just afraid

17:48.030 --> 17:50.070
Lord Zheng has a backup plan.

17:52.090 --> 17:52.830
Your Excellency,

17:52.830 --> 17:53.890
please watch this.

17:54.510 --> 17:55.970
Once this piece is placed,

17:57.200 --> 17:59.370
Your Excellency's advantage is gone.

17:59.540 --> 18:00.590
By then,

18:01.310 --> 18:03.550
it'll be hard to turn the tables.

18:08.590 --> 18:10.920
They say the chessboard
is like an empire.

18:10.920 --> 18:12.280
If I wasn't confident,

18:13.040 --> 18:15.240
would I have invited you to play with me?

18:22.830 --> 18:24.430
Lord Lyu, take a closer look.

18:25.160 --> 18:26.250
Who actually won?

18:33.350 --> 18:35.440
The 3-3 foul.

18:35.820 --> 18:37.670
This is against the rules.

18:37.920 --> 18:40.030
Who set the rule of the 3-3 foul?

18:41.270 --> 18:42.270
Well,

18:42.300 --> 18:43.950
it's been the rule

18:44.000 --> 18:45.550
since ancient times.

18:46.080 --> 18:47.970
This is clearly more straightforward.

18:47.970 --> 18:49.690
Why on earth is it illegal?

18:53.150 --> 18:53.990
Lord Lyu,

18:54.060 --> 18:55.480
let me ask you this:

18:56.000 --> 18:57.610
Dare you play a game with me

18:57.630 --> 18:59.890
and break these unreasonable old rules?

19:04.280 --> 19:05.240
OK.

19:11.670 --> 19:13.990
[Fan Hui,
Manager of the Affairs Bureau]

19:11.670 --> 19:14.370
Is the governor really impotent?

19:15.400 --> 19:16.860
Was your diagnosis wrong?

19:19.750 --> 19:21.210
To be honest, the governor

19:21.250 --> 19:22.310
is perfectly fine.

19:23.080 --> 19:24.500
He is not sick at all.

19:25.120 --> 19:26.480
Then why did you...

19:29.720 --> 19:31.350
Do you hold a grudge

19:31.350 --> 19:32.610
against the governor?

19:55.270 --> 19:56.030
It's...

19:56.940 --> 19:57.810
It's Lord Jiang

19:58.270 --> 19:59.810
who told me to do this.

20:01.520 --> 20:02.670
Am I, Jiang Shu,

20:02.690 --> 20:04.220
someone who holds grudges?

20:05.110 --> 20:06.030
Besides,

20:06.590 --> 20:09.420
based on your understanding
of the governor and his wife,

20:09.420 --> 20:11.310
and their personalities,

20:12.270 --> 20:15.930
is it really necessary for them
to make such a huge fuss about this?

20:18.520 --> 20:19.960
Then there must be

20:21.400 --> 20:22.720
more to the story.

20:25.590 --> 20:26.990
For everything unusual,

20:27.440 --> 20:28.840
there's always a motive.

20:29.350 --> 20:30.060
Moreover,

20:30.830 --> 20:32.940
Lord Zheng has been so aggressive.

20:33.330 --> 20:34.070
Tell me;

20:35.240 --> 20:36.540
if I exposed it,

20:37.230 --> 20:39.290
wouldn't I ruin the governor's plan?

20:45.520 --> 20:47.630
When I get back, I'll make you

20:48.330 --> 20:50.130
a sly and crafty mask.

20:57.350 --> 20:58.110
There.

21:00.270 --> 21:00.840
Right.

21:03.440 --> 21:04.160
Done.

21:04.200 --> 21:05.060
Dad.

21:05.550 --> 21:08.110
Stay out of the kitchen
from now on.

21:08.110 --> 21:09.110
Leave the cooking

21:09.110 --> 21:10.720
to Gao Ran and me.

21:11.200 --> 21:13.200
It's fine if you blew up the kitchen,

21:13.200 --> 21:15.350
but you almost blew yourself up today!

21:15.350 --> 21:16.880
Relax. I won't do it again.

21:16.880 --> 21:17.840
I promise.

21:17.940 --> 21:19.480
It's rare for Lord Fan to cook.

21:19.480 --> 21:21.280
He did very well for a first time.

21:21.320 --> 21:23.310
Be grateful
we don't have to eat it every day.

21:23.310 --> 21:24.880
If you want to eat it every day,

21:24.880 --> 21:26.310
no problem.

21:26.640 --> 21:27.470
I am

21:27.490 --> 21:28.690
going to resign

21:28.720 --> 21:31.040
and cook for you every day.

21:31.070 --> 21:32.680
What? Dad.

21:32.680 --> 21:34.400
You want to resign?

21:34.400 --> 21:35.310
Why?

21:35.310 --> 21:36.270
Like Gao Ran,

21:36.830 --> 21:37.790
I'm angry.

21:42.130 --> 21:44.330
Actually, my divorce with the governor

21:44.550 --> 21:46.160
isn't like what you think.

21:48.010 --> 21:49.340
It's not because of

21:49.830 --> 21:50.830
his dsyfunction?

21:52.350 --> 21:53.270
Then he must have

21:53.270 --> 21:55.060
found someone new, huh!

21:55.270 --> 21:55.990
Wait.

21:56.010 --> 21:59.670
With his dsyfunction, it's impossible
for him to find a new lover.

22:00.920 --> 22:02.050
After all that fuss,

22:02.350 --> 22:03.750
the governor likes...

22:04.330 --> 22:05.170
This is...

22:05.200 --> 22:05.960
Dad.

22:06.920 --> 22:07.980
It's not like that.

22:08.480 --> 22:09.030
Then...

22:10.240 --> 22:11.980
I'll just come clean with it.

22:12.330 --> 22:14.550
I asked for the divorce myself.

22:16.310 --> 22:18.590
Because I want to take the selection exam.

22:18.590 --> 22:21.520
-Take the selection exam?
-Take the selection exam?

22:22.360 --> 22:23.890
I want to become an official

22:24.070 --> 22:25.530
and serve the people well.

22:26.370 --> 22:27.130
Wait.

22:27.420 --> 22:28.980
Fan Yun, is this appropriate?

22:28.980 --> 22:30.680
Setting aside whether
the governor's reform will succeed,

22:30.680 --> 22:32.600
officialdom is a man's world.

22:32.720 --> 22:33.750
How can a weak woman like you

22:33.750 --> 22:35.400
outmaneuver those men?

22:35.440 --> 22:36.480
-Yes, yes.
-But...

22:36.480 --> 22:37.200
Gao Ran is right.

22:37.200 --> 22:39.120
What's so great about being an official?

22:39.120 --> 22:39.710
Besides,

22:39.730 --> 22:41.860
although our family is a bit poor,

22:41.890 --> 22:43.330
we can still make do.

22:44.240 --> 22:46.840
You don't need to
get involved in all that mess.

22:47.240 --> 22:49.270
Being an official is not an easy job.

22:53.830 --> 22:55.400
Do you also think

22:56.070 --> 22:57.600
I shouldn't take this path?

22:58.790 --> 23:00.350
Do you also think

23:00.350 --> 23:02.550
women are necessarily inferior to men?

23:03.630 --> 23:04.440
Dad.

23:04.650 --> 23:05.480
Gao Ran.

23:05.680 --> 23:06.920
I want to be an official,

23:06.920 --> 23:08.460
not just for myself.

23:09.480 --> 23:10.460
I want to

23:10.640 --> 23:12.240
set an example for everyone,

23:12.440 --> 23:13.480
so that all talents

23:13.480 --> 23:14.880
in the entire Nine Cities

23:14.880 --> 23:16.350
can serve the people.

23:18.380 --> 23:19.460
Yun,

23:19.560 --> 23:22.480
there's nothing wrong
with having lofty ambitions.

23:22.480 --> 23:23.480
B-But

23:23.480 --> 23:25.960
let's think this over carefully.

23:29.000 --> 23:29.460
No.

23:29.950 --> 23:30.600
Dad,

23:31.200 --> 23:32.200
my mind is made up.

23:35.310 --> 23:36.350
D-Dig in. Dig in.

23:36.350 --> 23:37.920
Let's eat. Let's eat.

23:41.240 --> 23:42.510
Let me try this.

24:08.920 --> 24:09.840
It's so late.

24:11.290 --> 24:12.330
Who could it be?

24:27.680 --> 24:29.570
Young... Young Master Qiyan?

24:30.510 --> 24:31.640
Why are you here?

24:32.910 --> 24:33.840
Are you free?

24:35.880 --> 24:36.880
It's a long night.

24:37.560 --> 24:39.020
Let me take you somewhere.

24:40.790 --> 24:41.400
Where to?

25:04.470 --> 25:05.270
Wait.

25:05.630 --> 25:07.310
When did our rooftop

25:07.400 --> 25:09.380
get so many flowers?

25:11.750 --> 25:12.550
Do you like it?

25:13.110 --> 25:14.680
I prepared it just for you.

25:17.000 --> 25:18.200
You prepared this?

25:19.250 --> 25:20.910
What's with all these flowers

25:20.960 --> 25:22.770
in the middle of the night?

25:24.260 --> 25:25.060
Besides,

25:25.340 --> 25:27.060
did you get my permission

25:27.340 --> 25:28.810
to decorate the rooftop?

25:29.240 --> 25:30.570
But your father agreed.

25:31.240 --> 25:32.310
When I told him

25:32.310 --> 25:33.880
I wanted to renovate the area,

25:33.880 --> 25:35.210
he agreed immediately.

25:36.350 --> 25:37.460
Goodness.

25:37.680 --> 25:38.940
I can't believe my dad.

25:43.940 --> 25:45.420
What brings you

25:45.450 --> 25:46.200
here today?

25:47.050 --> 25:48.380
There is a broader world

25:48.680 --> 25:50.140
outside the Qi Residence.

25:50.590 --> 25:52.440
You're no longer the governor's wife.

25:52.440 --> 25:54.970
How about I take you to
travel the Nine Cities?

25:55.000 --> 25:55.830
You

25:56.570 --> 25:57.570
and me?

25:59.240 --> 26:00.680
Why should I go with you?

26:03.510 --> 26:04.790
First, to relax;

26:05.350 --> 26:05.960
second,

26:05.960 --> 26:08.470
to consider what path to take
going forward.

26:08.730 --> 26:09.680
Besides,

26:10.640 --> 26:11.640
what's wrong

26:12.730 --> 26:14.170
with you and me?

26:20.180 --> 26:21.830
Thanks for your kind offer,

26:21.920 --> 26:22.750
but no thanks.

26:27.270 --> 26:28.200
And?

26:29.960 --> 26:30.790
And?

26:31.880 --> 26:32.720
And...

26:37.610 --> 26:38.940
Young Master Zheng Shi,

26:39.640 --> 26:40.810
why do you always

26:40.840 --> 26:42.400
dress up as Lou Qiyan?

26:45.720 --> 26:47.250
That's because Lou Qiyan is

26:47.640 --> 26:49.750
exactly the kind of person you want to be.

26:49.750 --> 26:50.750
That means that

26:51.380 --> 26:52.870
there's always a reason

26:52.900 --> 26:54.310
behind what you want to do.

26:54.310 --> 26:55.270
I'm the same.

26:55.800 --> 26:57.180
I, too, know the things I want to do

26:57.180 --> 26:58.640
and the person I want to be.

26:58.910 --> 26:59.970
Do you understand?

27:02.970 --> 27:04.050
Well,

27:04.590 --> 27:05.850
I'll go back to my room.

27:06.460 --> 27:07.710
You can...

27:08.660 --> 27:10.460
stay here and enjoy the flowers.

27:32.130 --> 27:33.000
Strange.

27:33.570 --> 27:34.890
Where is Fan Yun?

27:42.570 --> 27:44.040
Get your claws off her!

27:46.530 --> 27:47.640
Your Excellency?

27:52.110 --> 27:53.660
Why are you here too?

28:15.000 --> 28:17.860
Why did you visit so late at night,
Your Excellency?

28:21.880 --> 28:22.960
Some people

28:23.240 --> 28:24.700
just like climbing walls.

28:25.170 --> 28:26.650
Good thing I came in time.

28:27.100 --> 28:28.030
Otherwise, Fan Yun,

28:28.030 --> 28:29.630
you'd be taken advantage of.

28:34.200 --> 28:36.330
Fan Yun is now single without a spouse.

28:37.390 --> 28:39.310
As the governor,
you have a million things to do.

28:39.310 --> 28:41.410
Don't bother yourself with such trifles.

28:41.410 --> 28:43.510
If I'm concerned about it,
it isn't a trifle.

28:43.510 --> 28:46.040
Some people should
stop being so delusional.

28:51.480 --> 28:53.480
You're mistaken, Your Excellency.

28:54.120 --> 28:55.360
Young Master Zheng and I...

28:55.360 --> 28:56.990
Young Master Lou Qiyan and I

28:57.700 --> 28:59.040
are just friends.

29:00.150 --> 29:01.280
"Friends" are good.

29:02.240 --> 29:03.160
Being friends

29:04.100 --> 29:05.780
opens up more possibilities.

29:08.570 --> 29:11.030
Today, we're settling this
once and for all!

29:11.260 --> 29:12.260
Sure.

29:12.510 --> 29:13.840
That suits me just fine.

29:33.690 --> 29:35.750
Can you drink well, Your Excellency?

29:37.470 --> 29:38.820
More than well.

29:38.850 --> 29:40.330
I can drink like a sponge.

29:40.350 --> 29:41.420
This little wine

29:42.150 --> 29:43.260
is nothing.

29:46.790 --> 29:49.510
So settling things for you men

29:50.350 --> 29:51.810
means a drinking contest.

29:53.000 --> 29:53.590
Come on.

29:54.070 --> 29:55.800
According to my Ling'an rules.

30:23.240 --> 30:25.040
According to my Jing City rules,

30:25.410 --> 30:27.490
I toast Your Excellency
6 cups in return.

30:27.490 --> 30:28.330
Just 6 cups?

30:28.960 --> 30:30.620
Even 1,000 cups can't faze me.

30:49.570 --> 30:52.450
I've really never seen you drunk before,
Your Excellency.

30:52.450 --> 30:53.490
It seems

30:53.720 --> 30:55.480
even 1,000 cups can't faze you.

30:55.640 --> 30:56.880
Not just 1,000.

30:57.510 --> 30:59.370
Even 10,000 cups is nothing to me.

30:59.680 --> 31:00.540
Another round.

31:00.960 --> 31:03.070
Let me. Let me.

31:04.310 --> 31:05.320
Your Excellency,

31:05.440 --> 31:07.590
are you really going to drink 10,000 cups?

31:07.590 --> 31:09.030
Drinking too much

31:09.240 --> 31:10.500
is bad for your health.

31:11.350 --> 31:13.750
Are you sure you want to
keep drinking like this?

31:13.750 --> 31:16.010
We don't have that much wine
left at home.

31:17.750 --> 31:18.750
Did you hear that?

31:19.400 --> 31:21.480
Fan Yun is worried about my health.

31:23.720 --> 31:25.200
You can't handle your liquor,

31:25.200 --> 31:26.460
but you sure talk a lot.

31:26.470 --> 31:27.720
Can you do it or not?

31:27.880 --> 31:29.480
How dare you doubt me?

31:30.110 --> 31:30.800
Come on!

31:31.070 --> 31:31.750
Enough of that.

31:31.750 --> 31:32.830
Drink by the pot!

31:46.920 --> 31:47.920
Lou...

31:49.240 --> 31:50.480
What a surprise.

31:51.440 --> 31:52.240
I've known you for so long,

31:52.240 --> 31:55.370
-They're drunk.
-but I didn't know you can drink so much.

31:55.820 --> 31:58.010
Today, I've finally met my match.

31:58.970 --> 32:01.830
Your alcohol tolerance
is truly legendary as well.

32:02.160 --> 32:03.830
Why are they drinking so much?

32:04.850 --> 32:06.090
No idea.

32:06.810 --> 32:08.560
Look at how much wine is wasted.

32:10.030 --> 32:11.550
Tonight, I guess

32:12.000 --> 32:13.100
both of them

32:13.510 --> 32:14.480
won't be able to go home.

32:14.480 --> 32:15.740
But our house is small,

32:15.920 --> 32:18.050
with only one guest room. What do we do?

32:22.240 --> 32:23.200
Fan Yun.

32:24.160 --> 32:25.110
Fan Yun.

32:26.400 --> 32:27.510
I drank too much.

32:30.200 --> 32:31.390
I drank too much.

32:32.490 --> 32:34.060
Go home with me, OK?

32:37.480 --> 32:38.110
OK.

32:45.590 --> 32:46.510
Fan Yun.

32:48.200 --> 32:49.440
Fan Yun?

32:51.100 --> 32:51.970
Fan Yun.

32:52.700 --> 32:54.730
Don't go home with him.

32:55.020 --> 32:56.290
He has a dysfunction.

32:57.690 --> 32:59.100
Don't sleep with him.

33:00.000 --> 33:01.960
Stay far away from him.

33:02.920 --> 33:03.920
OK.

33:04.780 --> 33:05.980
He has a dysfunction.

33:06.030 --> 33:07.490
We won't hang out with him.

33:20.110 --> 33:21.710
-Why is it you?
-Why is it you?

33:21.790 --> 33:22.690
How do you know?

33:23.250 --> 33:24.390
How do I know?

33:24.790 --> 33:26.510
Who doesn't know that you divorced

33:26.510 --> 33:29.040
because of your bodily dsyfunction?

33:29.500 --> 33:30.500
You're insolent!

33:31.270 --> 33:32.310
I must punish you now.

33:32.310 --> 33:33.070
I'll skin you,

33:33.070 --> 33:34.310
and pull off your beard!

33:34.310 --> 33:35.480
Hurry, hurry!

33:35.480 --> 33:36.440
Don't fight! Don't fight!

33:36.440 --> 33:37.830
Your Excellency!

33:37.830 --> 33:39.200
Young Master Qiyan!

33:39.200 --> 33:41.750
Qi Zheng, so this is how you act
when you get drunk.

33:41.750 --> 33:43.640
No wonder Fan Yun divorced you.

33:44.350 --> 33:46.030
What does her divorce have to do with you?

33:46.030 --> 33:47.430
What on earth do you want?

33:49.770 --> 33:50.960
I want Fan Yun.

33:54.330 --> 33:55.440
Young Master Qiyan,

33:55.440 --> 33:56.970
what are you talking about?

33:57.000 --> 33:57.680
Get off me.

33:57.710 --> 33:59.030
I can't take it anymore.

33:59.030 --> 34:00.090
What are you doing?

34:02.030 --> 34:02.960
Look carefully.

34:03.350 --> 34:04.310
What is this?

34:05.550 --> 34:06.310
What's this?

34:09.199 --> 34:10.630
A grown man like you

34:10.650 --> 34:12.070
keeping a handkerchief at your waist.

34:12.070 --> 34:13.480
What's the deal with that?

34:13.480 --> 34:14.880
Fan Yun, tell him

34:14.880 --> 34:16.000
what this is!

34:16.440 --> 34:19.440
This is the handkerchief I gave you,
Your Excellency.

34:19.710 --> 34:20.710
Did you hear that?

34:21.400 --> 34:24.080
This is a token of love
that Fan Yun gave me.

34:24.110 --> 34:26.940
It has the phoenix flower of our love
embroidered on it!

34:26.940 --> 34:27.900
Do you have one?

34:29.110 --> 34:30.110
Your Excellency.

34:30.440 --> 34:32.070
What token of love?

34:32.880 --> 34:35.080
I don't have time for romance right now.

34:37.060 --> 34:37.830
Fan Yun.

34:38.590 --> 34:39.670
Look me in the eyes.

34:41.190 --> 34:42.320
Do you like me?

34:43.550 --> 34:44.320
I...

34:45.070 --> 34:45.840
I...

34:46.760 --> 34:47.280
I...

34:48.070 --> 34:49.070
Your Excellency,

34:49.230 --> 34:49.880
I...

34:52.780 --> 34:53.900
See?

34:55.710 --> 34:57.480
The delusional one

34:58.120 --> 34:59.160
is you.

35:00.150 --> 35:01.020
Fan Yun...

35:01.840 --> 35:03.390
Fan Yun likes...

35:06.670 --> 35:07.910
He's already drunk.

35:10.150 --> 35:12.510
A governor has a magnanimous heart.

35:12.530 --> 35:13.730
Sleep well, you punk.

35:17.960 --> 35:18.920
Fan Yun.

35:19.550 --> 35:20.920
I didn't lose!

35:21.310 --> 35:22.640
Right, you didn't lose.

35:23.440 --> 35:24.920
Your Excellency! You...
